      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个Docker服务的整体架构图。核心想法是Nginx作为统一入口，后面挂着code-server、Grafana和QuestDB这三个主要服务。",
      "elements_involved": [
