      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，Nginx做反向代理。那端口怎么分配？还有certbot是独立部署还是也放在Docker里？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "nginx",
        "certbot"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "全部容器化，所以把certbot也放进Docker Services这个子图里。Nginx暴露80和443，code-server用8080，Grafana用3000，QuestDB需要多端口——9000、9009、8812、9003。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "certbot",
        "nginx",
        "codeserver",
        "grafana",
        "questdb",
        "Docker Services"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，五个服务都放进Docker Services子图了，端口标注也加上了。现在画交互关系？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Docker Services",
        "codeserver",
        "grafana",
        "questdb",
        "nginx",
        "certbot"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对。User从外部访问，先连到Nginx。Nginx把请求路由到三个后端服务。另外code-server和Grafana都要读写QuestDB的数据。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
